WEBVTT

01:43.009 --> 01:46.090
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.130 --> 01:49.080
[Episode 17]

01:50.030 --> 01:51.350
The train is approaching.

01:51.870 --> 01:54.229
Please stand back and stay safe.

02:08.280 --> 02:09.759
Lu Yan, Lu Yan!

02:10.310 --> 02:11.200
Come on, get up.

02:13.860 --> 02:14.670
Are you okay?

02:16.180 --> 02:17.100
What's wrong?

02:17.670 --> 02:18.510
It's Ding Jing.

02:19.110 --> 02:19.700
What?

02:19.990 --> 02:21.430
It's Ding Jing.

02:23.750 --> 02:24.530
Okay.

02:24.920 --> 02:25.910
Are you hurt anywhere?

02:27.800 --> 02:29.380
I-I twisted my ankle.

02:30.570 --> 02:31.600
I'll take you out first.

02:32.110 --> 02:32.670
Let's go.

03:23.450 --> 03:24.210
Ding Jing.

03:40.390 --> 03:41.450
Who are you?

03:48.190 --> 03:49.829
[Huiting Complex]

04:11.550 --> 04:12.350
Are your hands cold?

04:13.040 --> 04:13.740
I'm fine.

04:17.860 --> 04:18.790
I'm still scared.

04:18.870 --> 04:19.529
You know...

04:21.110 --> 04:22.580
If I'd been a bit later...

04:26.030 --> 04:26.820
Sorry.

04:29.720 --> 04:30.560
Thank you…

04:31.830 --> 04:32.770
for protecting me.

04:46.530 --> 04:47.020
Hello?

04:47.460 --> 04:48.040
Captain Jiang.

04:48.500 --> 04:49.510
I checked the surveillance.

04:49.630 --> 04:50.360
It was someone

04:50.390 --> 04:51.630
in a dark gray hoodie

04:51.650 --> 04:52.630
who pushed Dr. Lu.

04:52.790 --> 04:53.890
But their face wasn't clear.

04:54.510 --> 04:55.630
Lu Yan said

04:56.070 --> 04:56.800
she saw the face.

04:56.830 --> 04:57.750
It should be Ding Jing.

04:58.430 --> 04:59.400
Look into Ding Jing.

05:00.060 --> 05:00.590
Got it.

05:01.210 --> 05:01.650
Alright.

05:07.150 --> 05:08.030
Ding Jing...

05:08.550 --> 05:09.190
is missing.

05:09.670 --> 05:10.510
But I think

05:11.790 --> 05:13.310
she might still try something.

05:14.830 --> 05:15.550
So,

05:16.120 --> 05:17.330
you need to be careful these days.

05:19.730 --> 05:20.890
At night,

05:21.510 --> 05:23.010
make sure to close all the doors and windows.

05:23.660 --> 05:24.710
If you're going to work,

05:25.050 --> 05:26.540
try to stick to a fixed route.

05:26.720 --> 05:28.090
Avoid places with few people.

05:28.110 --> 05:28.690
It's dangerous.

05:32.270 --> 05:33.230
Or maybe…

05:38.330 --> 05:38.890
Never mind.

05:40.700 --> 05:41.620
I'll stay here with you.

05:45.360 --> 05:46.659
I can…

05:47.080 --> 05:47.930
sleep outside.

05:48.560 --> 05:49.560
This way, I can be less worried.

05:51.840 --> 05:52.990
That's really unnecessary.

05:53.030 --> 05:54.730
You live right next door, don't you?

05:55.560 --> 05:56.680
If something happens,

05:56.720 --> 05:58.030
I'll just call out for you.

06:01.330 --> 06:03.280
Zhong accidentally spilled the beans yesterday.

06:06.160 --> 06:07.440
How's my cooking?

06:07.620 --> 06:08.400
Great!

06:10.030 --> 06:10.590
Come on, let's eat.

06:10.620 --> 06:11.750
Jiang is checking up on you, huh?

06:12.380 --> 06:13.500
Not checking up.

06:13.540 --> 06:15.960
Maybe it's just a call.

06:18.390 --> 06:19.200
Honey,

06:19.520 --> 06:20.960
can we talk about something?

06:20.990 --> 06:22.430
Next time you pull employees

06:22.430 --> 06:23.350
from my company,

06:23.630 --> 06:25.010
can you let me know first?

06:25.140 --> 06:26.460
I went in today, and there wasn't a single person.

06:26.490 --> 06:27.190
Even Dalu wasn't there.

06:27.210 --> 06:28.270
I was left all alone.

06:28.350 --> 06:29.690
Don't complain.

06:29.720 --> 06:31.440
I only asked him to help out.

06:31.710 --> 06:32.490
With what?

06:32.520 --> 06:33.370
None of your business.

06:33.390 --> 06:34.650
It's women's stuff.

06:36.290 --> 06:37.920
You took my employees away,

06:37.990 --> 06:38.909
and I'm the one paying their salaries.

06:38.909 --> 06:40.490
Of course it's my business.

06:40.680 --> 06:41.680
Now you're drawing a line

06:41.710 --> 06:42.860
between yours and mine?

06:43.270 --> 06:44.180
Listen.

06:44.210 --> 06:45.360
What's yours is mine,

06:45.409 --> 06:46.610
and what's mine is still mine.

06:46.630 --> 06:47.280
Got it?

06:47.409 --> 06:48.170
It's all yours.

06:48.350 --> 06:49.730
Fine, I'm petty.

06:49.820 --> 06:51.200
But at least I'm better than Jiang

06:51.270 --> 06:52.610
who's hiding things from Lu Yan.

06:55.670 --> 06:56.790
Hiding what?

06:56.990 --> 06:57.470
I... I...

06:57.550 --> 06:58.430
I'm going to cut some fruit.

07:06.330 --> 07:07.130
Actually,

07:07.150 --> 07:08.250
it's nothing.

07:08.740 --> 07:09.860
Just that

07:09.910 --> 07:11.540
Jiang had Zhong help him move.

07:11.710 --> 07:13.130
Jiang doesn't want you to know.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.200
Where did he move to?

07:16.590 --> 07:17.470
Next door to you.

07:21.200 --> 07:22.140
Next door to you.

07:23.390 --> 07:23.790
Next…

07:31.760 --> 07:37.530
[Play Back]

07:43.980 --> 07:44.610
Besides,

07:44.670 --> 07:46.030
the surveillance camera outside

07:46.150 --> 07:47.200
is not just for show.

07:47.240 --> 07:48.290
You think it can only catch bad guys

07:48.350 --> 07:49.480
but not you?

07:50.770 --> 07:52.720
You even gave me a goldfish.

07:56.510 --> 07:57.920
Zhong is just…

07:59.590 --> 08:01.270
He's so unreliable.

08:05.420 --> 08:06.300
I know

08:06.770 --> 08:07.950
you moved here…

08:09.420 --> 08:10.660
to protect me.

08:20.680 --> 08:21.310
It's okay.

08:21.340 --> 08:22.250
Now that I'm here,

08:22.470 --> 08:23.410
I can take care of you.

08:23.440 --> 08:24.860
It's hard for you to get around now.

08:25.860 --> 08:27.330
Once your injury heals, I'll leave.

09:01.850 --> 09:02.280
Hello.

09:02.310 --> 09:02.950
We're from the Criminal Investigation Unit

09:02.970 --> 09:04.170
of the Anshan District.

09:04.190 --> 09:05.390
Is this Ding Jing's home?

09:05.070 --> 09:05.770
[Public Security]

09:06.230 --> 09:06.900
Yes.

09:07.310 --> 09:07.870
Is she home?

09:08.880 --> 09:10.310
No. What's this about?

09:10.460 --> 09:11.040
Ma'am,

09:11.630 --> 09:12.530
Ding Jing is suspected of

09:12.630 --> 09:14.190
inciting assault

09:14.230 --> 09:14.890
and rape.

09:15.270 --> 09:16.530
This morning at the subway station,

09:16.600 --> 09:17.470
she attempted murder.

09:18.390 --> 09:19.190
Murder?

09:19.800 --> 09:22.050
[Summons]

09:19.960 --> 09:20.910
Here's the summons.

09:21.350 --> 09:22.100
Please cooperate.

09:22.250 --> 09:23.590
You must have the wrong person.

09:24.550 --> 09:25.510
Yes, officers,

09:26.070 --> 09:27.950
my daughter has a bad temper,

09:28.100 --> 09:29.440
but she'd never commit murder.

09:29.590 --> 09:30.270
Sir,

09:30.990 --> 09:31.530
Ma'am,

09:31.640 --> 09:33.150
I understand how you feel,

09:33.750 --> 09:34.750
but I hope you can

09:34.780 --> 09:35.670
face this

09:36.100 --> 09:37.030
and accept the facts.

09:37.510 --> 09:38.690
If Ding Jing returns,

09:38.830 --> 09:39.550
or if you hear anything

09:39.590 --> 09:40.510
about her,

09:40.750 --> 09:41.870
please contact us immediately.

09:43.110 --> 09:43.510
Okay.

09:44.070 --> 09:44.860
Okay, thank you.

09:45.150 --> 09:45.630
Thanks for your cooperation.

09:55.390 --> 09:55.990
Honey.

09:56.820 --> 09:57.670
Are you okay?

09:58.430 --> 09:59.340
It's you.

10:00.440 --> 10:02.830
It's all because of your irresponsibility.

10:03.590 --> 10:05.010
You ruined her!

10:05.070 --> 10:06.860
How could this be my fault?

10:35.150 --> 10:35.910
Are you asleep?

10:36.870 --> 10:37.550
No.

10:39.630 --> 10:41.510
Do you feel comfortable sleeping like that?

10:42.870 --> 10:43.560
I'm fine.

10:48.910 --> 10:49.640
Jiang Chengyi.

10:53.810 --> 10:54.580
Thank you.

10:56.040 --> 10:57.850
You thanked me several times today.

10:59.300 --> 11:00.400
I know.

11:02.060 --> 11:02.880
But you're always

11:02.910 --> 11:04.350
protecting me by my side.

11:05.390 --> 11:07.790
So I want to thank you again and again.

11:10.110 --> 11:11.200
I promised you

11:11.240 --> 11:12.320
a long time ago

11:12.390 --> 11:13.460
I'd protect you forever.

11:25.070 --> 11:26.570
Switch legs and stretch.

11:29.880 --> 11:30.950
Switch legs and stretch.

11:33.090 --> 11:33.990
Are you with me?

11:35.030 --> 11:35.770
What's wrong?

11:39.300 --> 11:39.910
What's wrong?

11:39.940 --> 11:40.800
You're upset?

11:43.630 --> 11:44.460
Jiang.

11:45.070 --> 11:46.030
I feel like

11:46.430 --> 11:47.930
someone's been following me lately.

11:48.390 --> 11:49.360
Following you?

11:50.720 --> 11:51.570
Where?

11:51.620 --> 11:52.460
What do they look like?

11:52.840 --> 11:54.940
I couldn't see what he looks like,

11:55.920 --> 11:57.480
but for the past couple of days,

11:57.500 --> 11:58.620
I've been taking random detours

11:58.640 --> 11:59.880
trying to catch a glimpse of him.

11:59.910 --> 12:01.030
But it seems he noticed

12:01.060 --> 12:02.230
and stopped following me.

12:03.280 --> 12:05.090
Maybe I'm just overthinking.

12:05.960 --> 12:06.850
Never mind.

12:09.340 --> 12:11.340
Still, since you feel that way,

12:12.580 --> 12:14.160
it's better to stay cautious

12:14.190 --> 12:15.230
to be on the safe side.

12:16.710 --> 12:17.570
How about this?

12:17.730 --> 12:19.150
Don't go running today.

12:19.530 --> 12:21.520
I'll teach you some

12:22.710 --> 12:23.500
self-defense moves instead.

12:27.360 --> 12:28.220
Grab like this.

12:28.240 --> 12:29.310
Hold him directly,

12:29.620 --> 12:30.510
pull his arm,

12:30.530 --> 12:31.110
and push him down.

12:31.340 --> 12:31.830
If you can't pin him down,

12:31.830 --> 12:32.320
and he's really strong

12:32.320 --> 12:33.070
and gets up,

12:33.070 --> 12:34.220
pull his arm away,

12:34.390 --> 12:35.530
and lock his neck.

12:37.490 --> 12:38.160
Got it?

12:38.900 --> 12:39.560
You feel it?

12:39.650 --> 12:40.110
Yeah.

12:40.190 --> 12:40.990
Really?

12:45.540 --> 12:46.210
Ouch, ouch!

12:46.230 --> 12:47.490
Push his hand down,

12:47.510 --> 12:48.250
press it,

12:48.270 --> 12:49.850
then circle around,

12:49.910 --> 12:51.710
and lock his neck from behind.

12:51.790 --> 12:52.500
Then slowly,

12:52.560 --> 12:54.190
tighten your arm.

12:54.910 --> 12:55.850
You feel it?

12:58.510 --> 12:59.550
Give it a try.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.240
Just like that.

13:03.060 --> 13:04.140
If he holds you,

13:05.250 --> 13:06.180
what do you do?

13:07.840 --> 13:08.470
What do you do?

13:08.510 --> 13:09.330
What... what do I do?

13:09.390 --> 13:10.580
Step out with your foot.

13:10.670 --> 13:11.590
If someone grabs you from behind,

13:11.630 --> 13:12.470
first, shift your body

13:12.510 --> 13:13.720
to create some space.

13:13.790 --> 13:15.400
Then grab his legs and toss him away.

13:16.790 --> 13:17.910
Use both hands to grab my legs

13:17.910 --> 13:18.560
and toss me away.

13:18.630 --> 13:19.560
Hold my legs and toss me!

13:19.600 --> 13:20.240
Toss, toss, toss!

13:23.080 --> 13:24.020
Got it?

13:26.030 --> 13:26.610
Yeah,

13:28.000 --> 13:28.550
I got it.

13:28.630 --> 13:29.150
Really?

13:29.500 --> 13:31.030
If you don't, I can't hold on any longer.

13:32.760 --> 13:33.480
But

13:33.640 --> 13:34.650
if you're in danger,

13:34.720 --> 13:35.650
you should run first.

13:35.710 --> 13:36.960
Don't try to fight them directly.

13:39.710 --> 13:40.750
Now that you've learned it, can you take me

13:40.750 --> 13:41.760
to the infirmary?

13:41.960 --> 13:42.650
What's wrong?

13:42.910 --> 13:43.510
Are you hurt?

13:43.550 --> 13:43.790
Yeah,

13:43.790 --> 13:44.470
I've fallen so hard

13:44.470 --> 13:45.220
that I can't move anymore.

13:45.250 --> 13:46.160
Which part of your body can't you move?

13:46.190 --> 13:47.270
I can't move at all.

13:47.590 --> 13:48.160
Really?

13:48.190 --> 13:48.720
Yeah.

13:48.900 --> 13:49.590
Then I…

13:50.750 --> 13:51.450
I…

13:58.620 --> 14:00.620
What is the goldfish doing?

14:05.420 --> 14:06.810
It's thinking about

14:07.080 --> 14:08.130
why you're still up.

14:11.390 --> 14:12.340
I'm going to sleep.

14:13.310 --> 14:14.090
Good night.

14:15.650 --> 14:16.240
Don't worry.

14:16.270 --> 14:17.310
I'm here.

14:18.110 --> 14:18.700
Good night.

15:32.630 --> 15:34.320
A-Are you cooking?

15:36.070 --> 15:36.780
You're up.

15:37.110 --> 15:38.230
Did I wake you up?

15:38.590 --> 15:39.340
No.

15:40.820 --> 15:42.190
Don't move. I'll help you.

15:45.250 --> 15:46.440
Don't move. I'll help you.

15:53.620 --> 15:54.240
Did you...

15:54.400 --> 15:54.950
make these?

15:55.110 --> 15:55.560
Yeah.

15:55.590 --> 15:57.030
I wanted to make a couple more dishes,

15:57.070 --> 15:57.670
but your fridge

15:57.710 --> 15:58.500
is practically empty.

15:59.480 --> 16:00.860
It held you back, huh?

16:01.800 --> 16:02.240
Come on.

16:02.260 --> 16:02.850
Eat up.

16:04.240 --> 16:05.310
How did you

16:05.360 --> 16:06.070
get such a bad bruise?

16:06.870 --> 16:07.550
I bumped into something yesterday.

16:07.590 --> 16:07.970
It's nothing.

16:08.080 --> 16:08.520
Eat your noodles.

16:08.550 --> 16:09.920
Why didn't you tell me?

16:21.710 --> 16:22.960
Rub this over it.

16:23.030 --> 16:24.220
It'll get much better.

16:24.610 --> 16:25.530
Where did you learn

16:26.530 --> 16:27.430
all this?

16:27.990 --> 16:29.230
I've been using this trick

16:29.310 --> 16:30.750
since I was little.

16:34.430 --> 16:35.030
Does it still hurt?

16:35.960 --> 16:37.090
Not at all.

16:37.390 --> 16:38.130
It really works.

16:46.430 --> 16:47.500
Alright, eat your noodles.

16:47.590 --> 16:48.190
They'll get soggy later.

16:48.230 --> 16:49.050
Rub a little longer.

17:04.579 --> 17:06.000
Have you got hold of Ding Jing?

17:07.910 --> 17:08.780
Still no sign of her.

17:09.190 --> 17:10.290
Don't worry about that.

17:10.319 --> 17:11.400
For now,

17:11.560 --> 17:13.030
I'll take you to and from work

17:13.140 --> 17:13.740
to keep you safe.

17:15.540 --> 17:17.040
What about my night shifts?

17:18.290 --> 17:19.369
No matter when you work,

17:19.400 --> 17:20.190
I'll give you a ride.

17:24.190 --> 17:25.170
Well,

17:25.500 --> 17:26.920
thank you then.

17:32.080 --> 17:35.780
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

17:38.000 --> 17:38.870
Alright.

17:39.480 --> 17:39.980
Well,

17:40.000 --> 17:41.230
I won't go in.

17:41.430 --> 17:42.740
Be careful at work.

17:42.770 --> 17:44.220
I'll pick you up after work.

17:44.430 --> 17:45.070
Got it.

17:45.090 --> 17:46.020
I'm not that delicate.

17:46.050 --> 17:47.100
Go do your thing.

17:47.630 --> 17:48.070
Listen.

17:48.110 --> 17:49.510
If you don't take care of the sprain properly,

17:49.670 --> 17:50.830
it could leave lasting effects.

17:51.070 --> 17:52.410
I'm a doctor, not you, okay?

17:53.000 --> 17:53.680
You're a doctor,

17:53.710 --> 17:54.670
but you still need to listen to me,

17:54.690 --> 17:55.280
understand?

17:55.750 --> 17:56.160
Okay.

17:56.260 --> 17:57.230
I'll listen to you.

17:57.430 --> 17:58.130
Alright, I'm off.

17:58.270 --> 17:58.810
Bye.

18:05.000 --> 18:06.460
-Lu.
-Morning, Yan.

18:07.310 --> 18:07.960
Morning.

18:08.020 --> 18:08.710
You... you two,

18:08.830 --> 18:09.430
you were just...

18:09.430 --> 18:10.230
inside?

18:10.750 --> 18:11.590
-No.
-Yes.

18:13.820 --> 18:14.820
-Yes.
-No.

18:20.760 --> 18:21.920
I'll get back to work.

18:21.990 --> 18:22.810
Very busy.

18:25.300 --> 18:26.640
What's with Matron Qiao?

18:26.660 --> 18:27.950
You made her mad?

18:28.050 --> 18:29.260
Yan,

18:29.330 --> 18:31.130
you only care about your love life.

18:31.860 --> 18:32.760
I'm off to work too.

18:32.940 --> 18:33.470
I...

18:37.700 --> 18:43.600
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

18:41.040 --> 18:42.120
It was indeed Ding Jing.

18:42.800 --> 18:43.790
After pushing Lu Yan,

18:43.830 --> 18:44.850
she ran out of the subway station.

18:49.500 --> 18:50.690
Then she went into this alley.

18:52.260 --> 18:53.040
She stayed in the alley

18:53.070 --> 18:53.870
for a few minutes

18:54.180 --> 18:55.710
before leaving from the other end.

18:55.950 --> 18:56.930
After that,

18:57.030 --> 18:58.340
she got into a ride-hailing car.

18:58.840 --> 19:00.270
I spoke to the driver.

19:00.510 --> 19:01.830
He said Ding Jing got off

19:01.880 --> 19:03.620
near Jifu Village.

19:05.900 --> 19:06.880
Where was her phone signal

19:06.900 --> 19:07.890
last detected?

19:08.190 --> 19:08.800
I've checked it.

19:09.030 --> 19:09.880
The last place it appeared

19:09.900 --> 19:10.630
was Jifu Village.

19:11.150 --> 19:12.090
We went there,

19:12.800 --> 19:14.080
but she wasn't there.

19:14.480 --> 19:16.500
Her phone was found in a trash can.

19:18.550 --> 19:19.570
Jifu Village

19:19.750 --> 19:21.340
doesn't seem like a place she usually goes.

19:22.660 --> 19:24.170
Throwing her phone in a trash can

19:24.200 --> 19:26.110
was likely to mislead us.

19:29.500 --> 19:30.270
You two,

19:30.300 --> 19:32.570
go take a look around Jifu Village

19:33.130 --> 19:34.580
and ask the locals

19:34.620 --> 19:35.560
if anyone's seen her.

19:35.630 --> 19:36.120
Got it.

19:36.140 --> 19:36.550
Got it.

19:37.420 --> 19:38.670
Have you checked her call records?

19:40.390 --> 19:42.330
From last night until now,

19:42.420 --> 19:43.640
she called Liu Yujie twice,

19:43.690 --> 19:44.790
but Liu Yujie didn't answer.

19:45.360 --> 19:46.840
One of the internet calls

19:46.910 --> 19:48.760
lasted about…

19:48.780 --> 19:49.760
a minute.

19:49.830 --> 19:51.850
The person she called the most is

19:52.150 --> 19:53.250
Yu Bofeng.

19:53.350 --> 19:54.520
Yes, Yu Bofeng.

19:55.270 --> 19:56.200
Yu Bofeng?

19:59.880 --> 20:01.210
Captain Jiang,

20:01.310 --> 20:02.070
you really don't see me

20:02.100 --> 20:02.790
as an outsider, huh?

20:04.110 --> 20:04.850
Yes,

20:05.030 --> 20:06.290
he did come to me earlier,

20:06.350 --> 20:07.730
saying he wanted to attend my class,

20:07.870 --> 20:08.600
but I've already

20:08.640 --> 20:09.910
turned him down.

20:13.280 --> 20:14.370
Alright, alright.

20:14.550 --> 20:15.420
I'll give it a try.

20:19.320 --> 20:28.940
[Walk into Yu Bofeng]

20:19.790 --> 20:20.900
So, Mr. Yu Bofeng,

20:20.910 --> 20:22.370
say something before we end this interview.

20:23.310 --> 20:24.270
I want to say to all

20:24.300 --> 20:25.990
the viewers who support me

20:26.160 --> 20:27.420
that I'll definitely work hard,

20:27.590 --> 20:28.280
stay true to my original intentions,

20:28.310 --> 20:30.020
and continue to bring you more

20:30.060 --> 20:30.740
and better work.

20:31.030 --> 20:31.840
Thank you all.

20:32.010 --> 20:38.690
[Walk into Yu Bofeng]

20:32.590 --> 20:33.070
Good.

20:33.150 --> 20:34.030
That wraps up

20:34.070 --> 20:34.860
this interview.

20:35.150 --> 20:36.280
We believe Mr. Yu Bofeng

20:36.310 --> 20:37.640
will achieve greater things in the future.

20:37.750 --> 20:38.270
Thank you, everyone.

20:38.430 --> 20:38.820
Goodbye.

20:39.150 --> 20:39.630
Goodbye.

20:41.150 --> 20:41.800
Thank you.

20:41.910 --> 20:42.700
Thank you.

20:46.720 --> 20:47.400
Alright.

20:47.760 --> 20:48.800
Thank you, everyone, for your hard work.

20:48.900 --> 20:49.640
Thank you.

20:49.730 --> 20:50.520
Thank you.

20:50.590 --> 20:51.190
Thank you.

20:51.310 --> 20:52.300
This way, please.

20:52.800 --> 20:53.600
Have some water.

20:53.810 --> 20:55.140
Talk with the cinematographer.

20:55.990 --> 20:56.440
Cinematographer,

20:56.470 --> 20:57.820
please confirm the lens number.

20:57.900 --> 20:59.200
Once it's confirmed,

20:58.600 --> 21:00.850
[Ms. Yu, are you free recently?]

20:59.230 --> 21:00.590
we'll send it straight to the editing room, okay?

21:15.040 --> 21:16.720
[Refuse] [Answer]

21:15.040 --> 21:16.720
[Professor Yu]

21:22.990 --> 21:24.580
Hello, Professor Yu,

21:24.960 --> 21:26.320
you finally picked up my call.

21:27.060 --> 21:28.130
Come to the teaching building

21:28.190 --> 21:29.450
within 20 minutes.

21:29.990 --> 21:30.870
20 minutes?

21:33.210 --> 21:34.110
If you can make it here

21:34.150 --> 21:35.270
within 20 minutes,

21:35.430 --> 21:36.760
I'll give you this opportunity.

21:43.820 --> 21:44.560
An,

21:46.640 --> 21:47.930
can I get to Ninghai Police Academy

21:47.990 --> 21:49.100
in 20 minutes?

21:49.570 --> 21:51.320
Are you kidding? 20 minutes?

21:51.840 --> 21:52.940
It's not far,

21:53.030 --> 21:53.950
about five kilometers or so.

21:54.030 --> 21:54.990
But if you go now,

21:55.030 --> 21:56.110
you'll be stuck in traffic for at least an hour.

21:59.700 --> 22:00.370
I have to get there first.

22:00.400 --> 22:00.980
There's no time.

22:01.510 --> 22:02.840
Your mic is still on!

22:12.980 --> 22:13.910
Unlocked successfully.

22:20.900 --> 22:23.160
[Lily Apartment]

22:24.610 --> 22:25.740
Unlocked successfully.

22:36.920 --> 22:37.760
The party membership fees

22:37.830 --> 22:38.900
and things like that…

22:38.950 --> 22:40.190
Collect what you need to collect.

22:40.300 --> 22:40.870
Alright.

22:40.890 --> 22:41.710
Okay, off you go.

22:41.790 --> 22:42.580
Alright, goodbye.

22:42.610 --> 22:43.170
Bye.

22:50.200 --> 22:51.160
Professor Yu!

22:52.190 --> 22:53.070
Professor Yu,

23:01.880 --> 23:02.860
I made it.

23:04.870 --> 23:06.680
Didn't expect you to be so punctual.

23:07.070 --> 23:08.180
Of course!

23:08.270 --> 23:09.730
I'm serious about attending your class.

23:11.780 --> 23:12.570
Follow me.

23:30.750 --> 23:31.970
Have a seat.

23:54.040 --> 23:55.430
Here's a résumé form.

23:55.450 --> 23:56.250
Fill it out.

24:08.350 --> 24:09.470
I really regret

24:09.490 --> 24:11.430
not slapping her a couple more times that day.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.670
How dare she push you?

24:12.670 --> 24:13.860
Is she crazy?

24:14.750 --> 24:16.130
Don't be so mad.

24:16.550 --> 24:16.910
Seriously,

24:16.910 --> 24:17.910
how can you laugh about this?

24:17.950 --> 24:19.130
Are you stupid or something?

24:20.020 --> 24:20.580
Anyway,

24:20.600 --> 24:21.830
right now,

24:21.880 --> 24:22.910
I'm really happy.

24:23.010 --> 24:24.750
If Ding Jing gets caught,

24:24.770 --> 24:26.550
everything will come to light.

24:26.700 --> 24:28.220
That's true,

24:28.500 --> 24:30.520
but you almost died.

24:30.540 --> 24:31.950
How can you just brush it off?

24:36.060 --> 24:36.830
Jiang Chengyi's here.

24:36.850 --> 24:37.730
I gotta go.

24:46.280 --> 24:47.240
Have you been waiting long?

24:47.270 --> 24:47.840
No,

24:47.870 --> 24:49.810
I was just going over some medical records.

24:49.830 --> 24:51.100
Any updates on Ding Jing?

24:52.280 --> 24:53.340
Not yet.

24:53.820 --> 24:54.950
But don't worry.

24:54.970 --> 24:55.960
She probably

24:56.100 --> 24:57.030
won't do anything for now.

24:57.610 --> 24:58.680
I'm not worried.

24:58.690 --> 24:59.940
I know you'll catch her.

25:03.320 --> 25:04.050
Let's go.

25:04.190 --> 25:05.470
Let's go home.

25:07.140 --> 25:08.270
Okay, let's go home.

25:12.010 --> 25:12.590
Done.

25:16.870 --> 25:18.290
Yu Bofeng.

25:19.240 --> 25:21.140
Male, 23.

25:24.650 --> 25:25.450
From the northeast, huh?

25:27.840 --> 25:29.110
After coming to Ninghai,

25:29.240 --> 25:31.430
you got signed by an agency.

25:32.950 --> 25:33.750
Not bad.

25:33.880 --> 25:35.230
You're luckier

25:35.270 --> 25:36.310
than most artists.

25:37.330 --> 25:37.820
I do

25:38.220 --> 25:39.710
consider myself lucky.

25:40.280 --> 25:41.310
I've never

25:41.310 --> 25:42.360
formally studied acting.

25:42.560 --> 25:43.990
I just happened to gain some attention.

25:44.790 --> 25:46.580
But if I keep filming like this,

25:46.800 --> 25:47.990
I'll eventually be eliminated.

25:48.270 --> 25:48.870
So, I want to

25:48.870 --> 25:49.830
become a good actor.

25:52.160 --> 25:53.410
To become a good actor,

25:53.430 --> 25:55.310
you should go to an acting coach.

25:55.660 --> 25:57.050
At most, I can only teach you

25:57.110 --> 25:58.890
basic theoretical knowledge.

25:59.020 --> 26:00.290
Will that help with

26:00.330 --> 26:01.450
your acting?

26:01.630 --> 26:02.240
The thing is, I've recently

26:02.260 --> 26:03.430
got an audition opportunity.

26:03.450 --> 26:04.220
I'll audition for

26:04.270 --> 26:05.540
a psychopathic serial killer.

26:06.020 --> 26:07.230
I really love that role.

26:07.470 --> 26:10.030
Besides, yesterday, I ended collaboration

26:10.070 --> 26:12.150
with a new brand on my own.

26:12.200 --> 26:13.700
If I don't land this role,

26:14.230 --> 26:14.700
my agency

26:14.750 --> 26:16.110
won't let me off the hook easily.

26:17.070 --> 26:18.160
So I need your help,

26:18.200 --> 26:18.850
Professor.

26:19.800 --> 26:22.110
Ending collaboration on your own?

26:22.140 --> 26:23.370
You've got quite the temper.

26:23.510 --> 26:24.840
What brand?

26:24.870 --> 26:25.750
They just let you off?

26:25.910 --> 26:26.870
The one in the news,

26:26.890 --> 26:28.110
Boya Porcelain.

26:28.750 --> 26:29.870
Its owner keeps calling me,

26:29.900 --> 26:31.180
but I'm not answering.

26:31.590 --> 26:32.110
I think

26:32.110 --> 26:33.190
her character is questionable.

26:33.440 --> 26:34.740
I don't want to work with her.

26:37.640 --> 26:39.060
You're pretty straightforward.

26:41.970 --> 26:42.640
So,

26:42.720 --> 26:43.750
Professor Yu, when can you

26:43.770 --> 26:44.540
start teaching me?

26:47.150 --> 26:48.070
This course

26:48.090 --> 26:49.040
might be a bit different

26:49.080 --> 26:50.270
from what you expect.

26:57.780 --> 26:59.470
Here's the presentation of my lesson plan.

27:00.910 --> 27:02.370
Take a look at it later.

27:02.870 --> 27:03.710
After you're done, write me

27:03.790 --> 27:05.150
a five-thousand-word reflection on it.

27:05.190 --> 27:06.000
Handwritten.

27:07.610 --> 27:08.390
Any problem?

27:11.430 --> 27:12.290
No problem.

28:06.230 --> 28:06.670
Feeling better?

28:06.710 --> 28:07.460
Does it still hurt that much?

28:07.700 --> 28:09.150
Much better.

28:19.540 --> 28:20.160
Careful.

28:21.360 --> 28:23.100
Why are you staying at my place?

28:23.430 --> 28:24.210
Don't get me wrong.

28:24.640 --> 28:25.530
I'm just worried you're hungry,

28:25.630 --> 28:26.650
so I'll cook for you.

28:26.760 --> 28:28.320
But I don't have any food at home.

28:28.590 --> 28:29.190
I've bought some.

28:29.210 --> 28:30.070
It'll arrive soon.

28:30.910 --> 28:31.510
Alright.

28:31.680 --> 28:32.710
You're my driver,

28:32.750 --> 28:33.550
and I cover your meals.

28:33.570 --> 28:34.160
Fair deal.

28:35.530 --> 28:36.750
I buy the food and cook it myself.

28:36.770 --> 28:37.610
How is that fair?

28:59.320 --> 29:01.290
It smells so good.

29:01.940 --> 29:02.770
You hungry?

29:04.540 --> 29:05.290
You wanna try a bite?

29:11.740 --> 29:12.530
Delicious.

29:15.190 --> 29:17.020
I didn't know you were such a good cook.

29:17.840 --> 29:19.100
Impressed?

29:19.560 --> 29:20.900
You looked pretty cool from behind,

29:20.930 --> 29:21.530
but when you said that,

29:21.590 --> 29:22.510
you sounded like a fool.

29:23.040 --> 29:23.780
Dr. Lu,

29:23.870 --> 29:25.070
can you please show some respect

29:25.090 --> 29:26.090
to the person who's so nice to you?

29:26.780 --> 29:27.270
Fine.

29:27.290 --> 29:28.400
Respect.

29:28.900 --> 29:29.590
Clear the table.

29:29.620 --> 29:30.280
Dinner is ready.

29:30.310 --> 29:31.640
I'll bring this over.

29:38.470 --> 29:39.220
Coming.

29:39.350 --> 29:40.100
All the dishes are here.

29:40.330 --> 29:41.240
Tomato and egg stir-fry.

29:41.270 --> 29:41.890
Yeah.

29:42.620 --> 29:43.310
Give it a try.

29:43.330 --> 29:43.920
Alright.

29:44.570 --> 29:46.120
It smells amazing.

29:51.080 --> 29:51.750
How's it?

29:53.160 --> 29:54.640
So tender.

29:54.760 --> 29:55.470
How did you make it?

29:55.510 --> 29:56.020
Teach me.

29:56.160 --> 29:57.000
No way.

29:57.160 --> 29:57.990
It's my family's secret recipe.

29:58.310 --> 29:59.540
So stingy.

30:00.080 --> 30:00.700
You know what?

30:00.880 --> 30:01.720
Back in the day,

30:01.850 --> 30:02.800
my dad used this dish

30:02.870 --> 30:03.610
to win over my mom.

30:27.870 --> 30:29.510
But I keep smelling

30:29.530 --> 30:31.130
a really delicious aroma.

30:31.660 --> 30:32.510
I don't think

30:32.530 --> 30:33.160
it's from these dishes.

30:33.190 --> 30:34.560
You made something else?

30:35.190 --> 30:36.300
Your nose is pretty sharp.

30:37.130 --> 30:37.980
It should be ready.

30:38.010 --> 30:38.930
The hidden menu.

30:38.950 --> 30:40.060
There's really another dish?

30:43.400 --> 30:44.290
What's it?

30:45.550 --> 30:46.290
A small pot.

30:46.390 --> 30:47.520
Take a look.

30:49.240 --> 30:50.210
Put it in the middle.

30:53.510 --> 30:54.750
Did you go to

30:54.880 --> 30:56.250
that malatang shop to buy it?

30:56.350 --> 30:56.800
Nope.

30:56.870 --> 30:57.580
I asked the lady there

30:57.630 --> 30:58.200
for tips

30:58.240 --> 30:59.430
and made it myself.

30:59.670 --> 31:00.610
You learned it?

31:00.730 --> 31:01.330
Try it.

31:07.350 --> 31:08.020
How is it?

31:08.190 --> 31:09.520
It tastes exactly the same.

31:16.830 --> 31:17.450
What are you staring at?

31:24.510 --> 31:25.680
It's so good.

31:48.030 --> 31:51.420
[Ninghai Police Academy]

32:01.100 --> 32:01.820
Professor Yu,

32:02.000 --> 32:02.600
you're off work?

32:02.980 --> 32:03.830
You haven't left yet?

32:03.850 --> 32:04.870
I just went to the restroom.

32:07.690 --> 32:08.310
Here.

32:11.990 --> 32:12.750
The reflection.

32:12.770 --> 32:13.560
Five thousand words.

32:13.990 --> 32:15.440
It turned out so great.

32:15.840 --> 32:17.410
I'm afraid it may get stolen, so I keep it with me.

32:29.870 --> 32:30.620
Professor Yu, so,

32:30.790 --> 32:32.440
can I come to your class now?

32:35.050 --> 32:36.490
I'll send you the class schedule later.

32:38.150 --> 32:39.200
Alright, thank you.

32:40.150 --> 32:41.150
For my class,

32:41.230 --> 32:42.040
you can't be late.

32:42.110 --> 32:43.360
Homework must be done.

32:43.590 --> 32:44.400
You might not keep up,

32:44.430 --> 32:45.780
but give it your all.

32:46.440 --> 32:46.970
Okay.

32:47.390 --> 32:47.880
Professor Yu,

32:47.910 --> 32:49.300
can you tutor me one-on-one?

32:56.470 --> 32:57.860
Thanks for today.

32:57.990 --> 32:59.140
The food was really delicious.

32:59.510 --> 33:00.370
Are you full?

33:00.990 --> 33:01.910
I'm stuffed.

33:02.580 --> 33:03.740
Want me to make you

33:03.950 --> 33:05.620
something else to eat?

33:06.630 --> 33:07.400
No.

33:07.670 --> 33:08.660
You should get going.

33:10.380 --> 33:11.320
Let me apply medicine for you.

33:12.040 --> 33:13.120
I've already done it.

33:13.190 --> 33:14.650
I'll be able to walk tomorrow.

33:17.560 --> 33:18.110
Alright.

33:20.020 --> 33:21.220
You need to do something later?

33:21.720 --> 33:23.080
I need to write a paper.

33:24.080 --> 33:25.330
Your arm is fine, right?

33:25.550 --> 33:26.600
Yeah, it's fine.

33:35.590 --> 33:36.680
Okay then,

33:38.020 --> 33:38.830
I'll head back.

33:43.120 --> 33:43.810
Bye-bye.

33:45.350 --> 33:46.090
Goodnight.

33:46.430 --> 33:47.080
Bye-bye.

33:52.320 --> 33:54.660
I've got a pile of dirty clothes at my place.

33:55.360 --> 33:56.030
Can I use your washing machine

33:56.070 --> 33:57.070
to wash them?

33:58.670 --> 34:00.780
You don't even have a washing machine

34:00.780 --> 34:01.440
at your place?

34:01.980 --> 34:02.550
Nope.

34:06.010 --> 34:06.550
Alright.

34:07.080 --> 34:07.870
I'll bring them over?

34:08.120 --> 34:09.060
Hurry up.

34:09.090 --> 34:09.750
Wait for me.

34:10.719 --> 34:11.389
Okay.

34:33.929 --> 34:34.960
Quick, quick, quick!

34:34.989 --> 34:35.710
It's freezing outside.

34:36.949 --> 34:37.650
Put them in.

34:40.449 --> 34:41.170
What's this?

34:41.230 --> 34:41.690
A tag.

34:41.830 --> 34:43.190
[Dry-cleaning tag]

34:42.679 --> 34:43.770
Dry-cleaning tag?

34:43.940 --> 34:44.850
This is clean.

34:45.820 --> 34:46.460
Really?

34:46.780 --> 34:48.310
It's been collecting dust for a while.

34:48.330 --> 34:49.199
I'll wash it again.

34:57.680 --> 34:59.280
There's one here too.

34:59.990 --> 35:01.510
This one is also clean.

35:01.830 --> 35:02.400
It…

35:03.360 --> 35:04.770
It smells. Wash it again.

35:11.640 --> 35:13.470
Then just use the quick wash.

35:13.500 --> 35:14.780
They're all clean anyway.

35:14.800 --> 35:15.460
I'll set it

35:15.490 --> 35:16.850
to a 15-minute quick wash.

35:17.970 --> 35:18.680
15 minutes.

35:18.790 --> 35:19.280
No, no, no.

35:19.310 --> 35:20.120
There are a lot of clothes.

35:20.150 --> 35:20.840
T-They need

35:21.030 --> 35:21.790
a longer wash.

35:21.830 --> 35:22.190
Let me see.

35:22.320 --> 35:23.330
Wait.

35:27.060 --> 35:28.950
The mixed wash will do.

35:28.970 --> 35:30.320
It's perfect for mixed clothes,

35:30.350 --> 35:30.980
isn't it?

35:58.260 --> 35:59.240
So complicated.

36:10.400 --> 36:11.240
I want to learn about it.

36:13.570 --> 36:14.780
Can you understand it?

36:15.590 --> 36:17.070
No, that's why I need to learn.

36:26.690 --> 36:32.240
[Wi-Fi] [Pass_Every_Exam_603]

36:27.180 --> 36:28.600
Which Wi-Fi network is yours?

36:29.230 --> 36:31.390
Pass_Every_Exam_603.

36:32.340 --> 36:32.780
What's the password?

36:32.400 --> 36:33.420
[Wi-Fi] [Password]

36:33.680 --> 36:36.310
20141229.

36:38.950 --> 36:40.110
2014…

36:41.030 --> 36:42.030
1229?

36:48.880 --> 36:50.230
♫As the city flickers♫

36:49.220 --> 36:51.220
I set this a long time ago.

36:51.240 --> 36:51.860
I…

36:51.570 --> 36:54.360
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

36:51.880 --> 36:52.920
I've been too lazy to change it.

36:55.560 --> 36:57.810
You've been living here that long?

36:55.640 --> 36:56.930
♫And you, who love to smile♫

36:57.950 --> 37:00.400
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

37:00.550 --> 37:01.440
All my passwords

37:01.430 --> 37:03.770
♫The humor of time♫

37:01.480 --> 37:02.280
are the same.

37:02.350 --> 37:03.080
I have a bad memory.

37:03.110 --> 37:03.950
I'm afraid I'll forget them.

37:04.150 --> 37:04.790
Okay?

37:05.270 --> 37:07.710
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

37:08.780 --> 37:14.540
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

37:10.430 --> 37:14.830
[Wi-Fi] [Password]

37:12.990 --> 37:13.750
Do you still remember

37:13.750 --> 37:14.670
what happened that day?

37:15.920 --> 37:17.540
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

37:18.650 --> 37:21.510
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

37:21.080 --> 37:21.990
Do you remember?

37:22.800 --> 37:24.230
♫The stubborn me♫

37:24.430 --> 37:25.520
Anyway, that day,

37:25.460 --> 37:28.160
♫I always think of the far future♫

37:26.200 --> 37:27.880
I posted something on my Moments.

37:28.940 --> 37:31.010
♫I walk willfully♫

37:31.990 --> 37:34.510
[December 29, 2014]

37:32.390 --> 37:35.310
♫Like a star revolving around♫

37:35.950 --> 37:37.260
♫I turn around♫

37:38.420 --> 37:41.920
♫But you're not behind me♫

37:58.490 --> 38:01.640
[Public Security]

38:01.940 --> 38:07.530
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

38:07.840 --> 38:08.230
Jiang.

38:10.700 --> 38:12.370
We visited all the small inns

38:12.480 --> 38:13.350
around Jifu Village.

38:13.880 --> 38:14.400
In the village,

38:14.430 --> 38:15.970
we went door to door searching as well.

38:16.340 --> 38:16.940
No sign of her.

38:17.670 --> 38:19.220
What about nearby transport hubs?

38:19.310 --> 38:20.580
Long-distance buses or anything like that?

38:20.600 --> 38:21.560
I've asked

38:21.600 --> 38:22.820
the local drivers

38:22.910 --> 38:23.600
and ticket sellers.

38:23.630 --> 38:24.390
None of them have seen Ding Jing.

38:25.560 --> 38:27.110
The area around Jifu Village

38:27.130 --> 38:28.430
is mostly farmland.

38:28.750 --> 38:30.160
The few roads there

38:30.180 --> 38:31.020
don't have surveillance cameras.

38:31.070 --> 38:31.870
It's really hard to track her.

38:32.510 --> 38:33.310
Judging from the map,

38:33.350 --> 38:34.830
the transportation around Jifu Village

38:35.430 --> 38:37.150
isn't very developed.

38:39.180 --> 38:40.650
She shouldn't have gotten very far.

38:44.190 --> 38:45.270
Send a few more people,

38:45.390 --> 38:46.870
expand the search area,

38:46.990 --> 38:48.010
and search again.

38:48.270 --> 38:49.500
I don't believe she could have gotten away.

38:49.750 --> 38:50.120
Understood.

38:50.150 --> 38:50.470
Got it.

38:50.590 --> 38:50.870
Let's go.

38:54.960 --> 38:56.080
This one…

38:56.420 --> 38:57.370
I haven't seen her before.

38:59.760 --> 39:00.860
This one looks familiar,

39:00.900 --> 39:02.340
but I forgot which day it was.

39:02.550 --> 39:03.540
She booked a room

39:03.670 --> 39:04.230
but left

39:04.280 --> 39:05.020
without checking in.

39:06.670 --> 39:08.070
No records about her.

39:08.800 --> 39:09.720
Nothing at all?

39:09.840 --> 39:10.230
Nothing.

39:10.870 --> 39:11.230
Alright.

39:11.250 --> 39:12.290
Copy all the surveillance footage

39:13.030 --> 39:13.630
and take it back.

39:13.710 --> 39:14.880
See if there are any useful clues.

39:15.360 --> 39:15.960
Okay.

39:16.310 --> 39:17.380
Officer,

39:17.590 --> 39:19.240
I'm just running a small business here.

39:19.670 --> 39:20.630
Sometimes, to make things simple

39:20.670 --> 39:21.310
for the customers,

39:21.580 --> 39:22.510
we skip the registration process.

39:31.350 --> 39:32.240
It won't happen again.

39:35.630 --> 39:36.740
Booking a room without checking in.

39:36.760 --> 39:38.290
Either she felt this place wasn't safe,

39:38.430 --> 39:39.670
or she wanted to leave some clues

39:39.720 --> 39:40.870
to deliberately mislead us.

39:41.610 --> 39:42.080
Here's the plan:

39:42.110 --> 39:43.340
have the team put in a bit more effort,

39:43.390 --> 39:43.830
expand the search area,

39:43.880 --> 39:45.470
and cover the entire outskirts.

39:46.050 --> 39:46.680
Okay.

39:46.910 --> 39:49.880
[Outpatient]

40:04.720 --> 40:05.340
Yan.

40:05.510 --> 40:06.650
Lin Xiaoman is scared of the surgery.

40:06.780 --> 40:07.760
He's been hiding in the restroom,

40:07.790 --> 40:08.310
refusing to come out.

40:08.950 --> 40:09.870
Let's go take a look.

40:09.960 --> 40:10.630
Okay.

40:12.520 --> 40:13.230
Xiaoman,

40:13.260 --> 40:14.350
open the door, Xiaoman.

40:14.390 --> 40:15.220
Be good.

40:16.190 --> 40:17.560
Xiaoman, come out now!

40:17.630 --> 40:18.100
Xiaoman!

40:18.390 --> 40:19.560
I don't want surgery!

40:19.670 --> 40:20.740
I don't want surgery!

40:20.770 --> 40:21.730
Xiaoman,

40:21.830 --> 40:22.510
once the surgery's done,

40:22.510 --> 40:23.240
you'll get better

40:23.270 --> 40:24.190
and be healthy again.

40:24.750 --> 40:25.430
Lin Xiaoman,

40:25.550 --> 40:27.190
this is my last warning.

40:27.360 --> 40:28.530
If you don't come out, I'll hit you!

40:28.560 --> 40:29.710
Can't you speak nicely?

40:29.830 --> 40:30.510
Don't scare him, okay?

40:30.510 --> 40:31.510
I don't want it!

40:35.470 --> 40:35.990
Lu Yan.

40:38.990 --> 40:40.110
Coming through.

40:40.140 --> 40:41.280
Let me handle it.

40:43.990 --> 40:44.550
Xiaoman,

40:45.350 --> 40:46.830
it's me, Ms. Lu.

40:47.070 --> 40:48.390
I'm your anesthesiologist.

40:49.510 --> 40:50.790
Trust me, okay?

40:50.870 --> 40:51.990
I'll keep you safe.

40:52.360 --> 40:54.230
But I'm scared.

40:54.630 --> 40:55.430
Don't be scared.

40:55.670 --> 40:56.990
I promise it won't hurt,

40:57.010 --> 40:57.760
okay?

40:58.400 --> 41:00.240
I brought you a gift.

41:00.510 --> 41:01.710
Look, what's it?

41:02.180 --> 41:03.710
Yeah, come out and look!

41:03.890 --> 41:04.680
Xiaoman.

41:07.890 --> 41:09.540
Look, it's chocolate, isn't it?

41:09.950 --> 41:10.580
You're getting

41:10.670 --> 41:11.550
bolder now, huh?

41:11.830 --> 41:12.500
Let go of me!

41:12.860 --> 41:13.670
I don't want surgery!

41:13.920 --> 41:14.820
I don't want surgery!

41:14.980 --> 41:15.610
What are you doing?

41:15.630 --> 41:16.630
You can't hit him!

41:16.630 --> 41:17.620
Step aside!

41:18.320 --> 41:18.990
Get up!

41:19.600 --> 41:20.600
Don't hit the child!

41:20.630 --> 41:21.510
Don't hit the child!

41:21.630 --> 41:23.060
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

41:23.990 --> 41:24.830
What are you doing?

41:26.540 --> 41:27.560
Why did you hit him?

41:28.460 --> 41:29.530
Why did you hit him?

41:29.800 --> 41:30.790
Who are you to hit him?

41:30.830 --> 41:31.940
Someone, help!

41:32.260 --> 41:33.580
Stop! Stop! Stop!

41:33.760 --> 41:34.600
Help!

41:36.110 --> 41:37.030
Security!

41:37.440 --> 41:38.400
Help!

41:51.310 --> 41:52.270
Wen.
